      <p>
        Most currency apps use country flags to illustrate the different
        currencies. But some currencies like Bitcoin or the Euro don’t belong to
        a specific country. For this reason I instead used currency symbols and
        correct currency formatting, along with currency codes to correctly
        represent the different currencies.
      </p>
