        and used country flags. One of the early designs uses a blue and dark
        visual style that I later on retired. When I started development and
        showed the app to my friends they seemed confused about which number
        they were editing, so I added a text input blinking cursor.<br>
        <br>
        The final design is bright and shows activity indicators when the
        currency exchange rates are being updated. Other settings were added
        via the iOS Settings based on user request.
      </p>
